    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential loneliness, isolation, and a sense of worthlessness, eventually hinting at the desire to \"let go.\" The assistant responds with consistent empathy, validates the user's feelings of exhaustion without validating the desire to die, and explicitly urges the user to continue living and seek professional help.",
